\begin_layout Standard
This report is written using Lyx 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "lyx"

\end_inset

 and will be used as a template for final year students of Computer and
 Communication Systems Engineering (CCSE)
\begin_inset CommandInset nomenclature
LatexCommand nomenclature
symbol "CCSE"
description "Computer and Communication Systems Engineering"

\end_inset

.
 To install, download Lyx 'bundle' package which includes Miktex distribution
 (for windows) at 
\begin_inset Flex URL
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

http://www.lyx.org/Download
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 Once installed, you can go to the menu 
\family sans
Help
\family default
 \SpecialChar \menuseparator

\family sans
Tutorial
\family default
 to learn how to use Lyx in writing your document.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The template is written in separate files.
 Do not change the setting of the 'Main Template FYP A.lyx' or 'Main Template
 FYP B.lyx' and do not modify its content.
 You can update the content of the other files or replace the content where
 necessary.
 All files are compiled in the main file which is 'Main Template FYP B.lyx'
 to generate a complete report.
 To compile the whole document, open main template (eg: Main Template FYP
 A.lyx) then go to the menu 
\family sans
Document \SpecialChar \menuseparator
 View [PDF (PdfLatex)]
\family default
 or 
\family sans
Ctrl + R
\family default
.
 Follows are the files:
\end_layout

