\begin_layout Section
Figures
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To insert a figure, first you need to insert float figure and then insert
 graphics inside the float.
 Go to the menu 
\family sans
Insert
\family default
 \SpecialChar \menuseparator

\family sans
Float
\family default
 \SpecialChar \menuseparator

\family sans
Figure
\family default
 or you can use the toolbar button 
\begin_inset Info
type  "icon"
arg   "float-insert figure"
\end_inset

.
 Then put a cursor inside the float before the caption and go to the menu
 
\family sans
Insert
\family default
 \SpecialChar \menuseparator

\family sans
Graphics
\family default
.
 Note that the figure must appear above the caption of the figure.
 The detail including examples can be found in the menu 
\family sans
Help
\family default
 \SpecialChar \menuseparator

\family sans
EmbeddedObjects.
 
\family default
If you want to put citation inside a figure or a table, you need to replace
 the default caption.
 Go to 
\family sans
Insert
\family default
 \SpecialChar \menuseparator

\family sans
Tex Code
\family default
 or press Ctrl + L and type in the following:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\backslash
caption[Caption for list entry]{the content 
\backslash
cite{lyx} 
\backslash
label{fig:XXX}}
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Image Formats
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
You can use different image formats.
 However, the best format is eps format based on the comparison as shown
 in Figures 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:pdfformat"

\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:jpgformat"

\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:epsformat"

\end_inset

.
 Note that the figures have been scaled down to 35% to fit onto one page.
 The figures are created using Matlab plot function and saved as in the
 respective formats.
 You can use any free softwares such as GIMP to convert any image formats
 to eps.
 You can change the placement of figures by right click the float figure
 and choose 
\family sans
Settings
\family default
.
\end_layout

