\begin_layout Standard
You can insert a table using either the toolbar button 
\begin_inset Info
type  "icon"
arg   "tabular-insert"
\end_inset

 or the menu 
\family sans
Insert\SpecialChar \menuseparator
Table
\family default
.
 The detail including examples can be found in the menu 
\family sans
Help
\family default
 \SpecialChar \menuseparator

\family sans
EmbeddedObjects
\family default
.
 If your table is written in Microsoft Excel, you can convert it to Latex(plain)
 and then import to Lyx using 
\family sans
Excel2LaTeX.
 
\family default
To align the table to center, inside the table float, right click, choose
 
\family sans
Paragraph settings
\family default
, and set the Alignment to Centered.
 The example of table rotate to sideways is shown in Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "tab:Table-Example"

\end_inset

.
